					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Early in development, but playable. Source code included, builds with asm6.<br /><br />I used sprite layering to add more color to the enemies, causing sprites to drop out. The selection cursors will be moved to the background, and AI adjusted to avoid Y alignments.<br /><br />Graphics: <a href="https://opengameart.org/content/16x16-fantasy-tileset" class="postlink">16x16 Fantasy tileset</a> by Jerom licensed CC-BY-SA 3.0<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">Controls:<br />&nbsp;D-Pad: Move<br />&nbsp;A: Ranged Attack (if available)<br />&nbsp;Select: Toggle Inventory<br /></div><br /><br />Most glaring issues:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">; bugs:<br />;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;- enemies can move into player square without attacking<br />;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;- sprite drop out<br />;<br />; to do:<br />;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;- give bosses their own AI<br />;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;- adjust balance<br />;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;- add music/sfx<br /></div></div>

					
